Title: Lucky Strike
Plot: After a man driving with a wooden stake in his head dies in front of a casino, Grissom and Nick work to discover the 'vampire' killer. Warrick and Catherine hunt for the killer of an NBA star's 5 year old son.
GuestStars: Dwayne Adway, Tracy Middendorf, Leslie Silva, Mahershalalhashbaz Ali, Cameron Daddo, Sam Jaeger, Loren Lazerine, Christina Christian, Tequan Richmond, Alexandra Lee, Jimm Giannini, Steffon Sam
